---

<Layout>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative flex items-center min-h-[320px] w-full bg-cover bg-center py-[50px]" style={`background-image: url(${page_header_bg_img.src})`}>
        <div class="relative container mx-auto px-5 text-left">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-white">
                Program do wystawiania faktur, Faktura VAT 2026 START
            </h1>
            <div class="flex text-white text-sm font-semibold uppercase mt-5">
                <a href="/" class="hover:underline">Strona główna</a>
                <span class="px-2">»</span>
                <span>Program do wystawiania faktur, Faktura VAT 2026 START</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-6xl">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8">
            <!-- Main Content -->
            <div class="lg:w-2/3">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Program do wystawiania faktur. Faktura VAT 2026 START</h2>
                
                <div class="prose max-w-none">
                    <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 mb-6">
                        Faktura VAT 2026 START to nowoczesny i prosty program do wystawiania faktur dla systemów Windows. 
                        Dla użytkowników, którzy potrzebują jedynie prostego programu do faktur przygotowaliśmy wersję START. 
                        Umożliwia wystawienie niezbędnych dokumentów sprzedaży i zakupu, min. faktury VAT, bez VAT, korekty, 
                        paragony, rachunki, oferty, zamówienia...
                    </p>

                    <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 mb-8">
                        Wygodna i prosta obsługa programu pozwala na pracę osobą, które posiadają małe doświadczenie z komputerem, 
                        niskim nakładem czasu umożliwi pracę i obsługę w małej bądź średniej firmie. 
                        Idealne rozwiązanie dla małych i średnich firm handlowo-usługowych. Generowanie pliku JPK.
                    </p>

                    <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Program do wystawiania faktur: Podstawowa funkcjonalność</h3>
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <ul class="space-y-2">
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Wystawianie dokumentów sprzedaży</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Kasa i Przelewy</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Cennik, Lista kontrahentów</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Ewidencja VAT i Raport sprzedaży</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <ul class="space-y-2">
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Import i Eksport</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Archiwizacja danych</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Plik JPK</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-12">
                        <img 
                            src={StartImg.src} 
                            alt="Faktura VAT - program do wystawiania faktur w wersji START" 
                            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-gray-200"
                            width="639" 
                            height="517"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center">Interfejs programu Faktura VAT 2026 START</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 mb-8">
                        <div class="flex">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div class="ml-3">
                                <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
                                    <strong>WAŻNE:</strong> NASZE PROGRAMY ZAWSZE ZGODNE Z NOWYMI PRZEPISAMI! Faktura JPK (Plik JPK v7). Mechanizm podzielnej płatności – Split payment, VAT OSS, GTU.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Faktura VAT 2026 START - opis funkcji</h2>

                    <!-- Features Accordion -->
                    <div class="space-y-4 mb-12">
                        {features.map((feature, index) => (
                            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden" x-data="{ open: false }">
                                <button 
                                    @click="open = !open"
                                    class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left font-medium text-gray-700 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 flex justify-between items-center"
                                    :aria-expanded="open"
                                >
                                    <span>{feature.title}</span>
                                    <svg 
                                        class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform duration-200" 
                                        :class="{ 'rotate-180': open }"
                                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
                                        viewBox="0 0 20 20" 
                                        fill="currentColor"
                                    >
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                    </svg>
                                </button>
                                <div 
                                    x-show="open" 
                                    x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200"
                                    x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0"
                                    x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100"
                                    x-transition:leave="transition ease-in duration-150"
                                    x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100"
                                    x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0"
                                    class="px-6 py-4 bg-white border-t border-gray-200"
                                    x-cloak
                                >
                                    <div class="prose max-w-none" set:html={feature.content} />
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        ))}
                    </div>

                    <!-- Customer Reviews -->
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Opinie naszych klientów</h3>
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                            {reviews.map((review, index) => (
                                <div key={index} class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                                    <div class="text-yellow-400 mb-3">
                                        {[...Array(5)].map((_, i) => (
                                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 inline-block" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                                <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
                                            </svg>
                                        ))}
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic">"{review.text}"</p>
                                    <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">{review.author}</p>
                                </div>
                            ))}
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Call to Action -->
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Zainteresowany naszym programem?</h3>
                        <p class="mb-6">Pobierz wersję demonstracyjną lub kup pełną wersję już teraz!</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
                            <a href="/bezplatne-wersje-demonstracyjne/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition-colors">
                                Pobierz wersję demonstracyjną
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://ksiegowosc24.pl/sklep/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-blue-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition-colors">
                                Kup teraz
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Sidebar -->
            <div class="lg:w-1/3 space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-white p-6">
                    <img 
                        src={StartImg.src} 
                        alt="Faktura VAT 2026 START" 
                        class="w-full h-auto mb-4 rounded"
                        width="220" 
                        height="244"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                    <div class="space-y-3 text-[16px] uppercase">
                        <a href="/bezplatne-wersje-demonstracyjne/" class="block w-full text-center px-4 py-3 bg-[#eee] hover:bg-[#008292] text-[#222] hover:text-white font-medium transition-colors">
                            Pobierz program
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://ksiegowosc24.pl/sklep/" class="block w-full text-center px-4 py-3 bg-[#eee] hover:bg-[#008292] text-[#222] hover:text-white font-medium transition-colors">
                            Kup teraz
                        </a>
                        <a href="/cennik-faktura-vat/" class="block w-full text-center px-4 py-3 bg-[#eee] hover:bg-[#008292] text-[#222] hover:text-white font-medium transition-colors">
                            Porównaj wersje
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Potrzebujesz pomocy?</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Nasi konsultanci są do Twojej dyspozycji od poniedziałku do piątku w godzinach 8:00 - 16:00</p>
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <div class="flex items-center">
                            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
                            </svg>
                            <a href="tel:+48123456789" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">+48 12 345 67 89</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center">
                            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                            </svg>
                            <a href="mailto:biuro@rafsoft.pl" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">biuro@rafsoft.pl</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<!-- Alpine JS for accordion functionality -->
<script src="//unpkg.com/alpinejs" defer></script>

<style>
    [x-cloak] { display: none !important; }
    .prose ul > li {
        margin: 0.5em 0;
    }
    .prose ul {
        margin: 1em 0;
        padding-left: 1.5em;
    }
</style>
